data.description: Great three-bedroom two bath home in the desirable Southgate subdivision located in the award-winning Carolina Forest school district!  This residence features laminate and tile throughout.  The master bedroom is on the first floor.  The exterior of the home has front and rear covered patios, utility shed with plenty of storage, one car garage and a large, private fenced back yard!  The neighborhood has a pool, playground and a large, covered patio for your enjoyment!  This ideal location is close to the beach, shopping, dining, entertainment, Coastal Carolina University, Horry Georgetown Technical College and world class golf.  With easy access to highway 501 and 31 be anywhere in minutes!  Contact your agent to schedule a showing today!
